üìç LOCATION 1: Gateway Router (Most Important!)
What to Summarize:

Combine Douala (10.1.1.0/24) + Yaounde (10.1.2.0/24) = 10.1.0.0/23
Combine Garoua (10.2.1.0/24) + Maroua (10.2.2.0/24) = 10.2.0.0/2

! ========================================
! GATEWAY ROUTER - ROUTE SUMMARIZATION
! ========================================

enable
configure terminal

! STEP 1: Remove old specific routes
no ip route 10.1.1.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.2
no ip route 10.1.2.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.2
no ip route 10.2.1.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.6
no ip route 10.2.2.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.6

! STEP 2: Add summary routes
! Summary for R1's LANs (10.1.1.0/24 + 10.1.2.0/24)
ip route 10.1.0.0 255.255.254.0 10.0.0.2

! Summary for R2's LANs (10.2.1.0/24 + 10.2.2.0/24)
ip route 10.2.0.0 255.255.254.0 10.0.0.6

! STEP 3: Keep distribution network routes (optional)
ip route 172.16.10.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.2
ip route 172.16.11.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.2
ip route 172.16.20.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.6
ip route 172.16.21.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.6

end
write memory
